A version of the Prusa Talking Claptrap (CL4P-TP) using an Adafruit Trinket M0 microcontroller and a five RGB Neopixel "eye".
Should work with minimal changes for other SAMD21 devices by updating pin settings.


See original project:
https://www.prusaprinters.org/prints/34222-talking-claptrap-cl4p-tp/

Trinket M0:
https://www.adafruit.com/product/3500

Powerboost 1000 Charger:
https://www.adafruit.com/product/2465
(conveniently makes Claptrap rechargeable with a Lipo battery)


